// This isn't really a page. This is server-side code that executes
// when someone visits /merch and instantly redirects them to the Humo store.
// 
// Since we set Astro to output 'static' but still dynamically routes
// some endpoints, we can configure redirects perfectly natively.

return Astro.redirect('https://humointernacional.com/tienda/artista-ramper/', 302);
